2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper focuses on relay networks, which are an important component of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with the behavior of relay systems, which can be analyzed using systems and control theory. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper mentions the use of massive MIMO systems, which are commonly used in multimedia applications. 
5. cs.COM (Computers and Society): Although less likely, the paper may also touch upon the societal implications of using inexpensive transceivers with hardware impairments in communication systems.
